00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:40.880
Teman-teman, harap serius.
Mama..

00:06:41.400 --> 00:06:43.240
Pelan-pelan..
- Oke..

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:46.440
Bu, berikan sedikit energi lagi.
- Ayo.

00:06:46.520 --> 00:06:48.560
Lima, enam, tujuh, delapan.

00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:59.800
Apa langkah selanjutnya.. - Oke..
